A4.text: Stig Anderson was the manager of the Hootenanny Singers and founder of Polar Music, but there is no mention of him being a member of The Beatles, Roxette, Ace of Base, or ABBA.

A5.text: Sometimes referred to as the 'fifth member' of ABBA
